libkinect_aux
=============

About
----------------------------------------
Kinect Auxiliary Library
Provides easy access to kinect acceleration sensor, motor and LED.

Requirements
----------------------------------------
 - CMake
     http://cmake.org/
 - libusb
     http://www.libusb.org/

Compilation
----------------------------------------
 - mkdir build && cd build
 - cmake -D CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release ..
 - make
